{"tid":1492774,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[粵塾再請人喇！] 想請一個 作家/寫手 寫香港傳奇人物嘅故事","createTime":"2019-08-21T03:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T05:42:13.000Z","uid":223799,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e51fb894ea9fe36c1a2cec96749c577d1a1775fc","tid":1492774,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wjg8SRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjg8SRM.jpg&h=51a8c5a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抱住向世界推廣廣東話同香港文化嘅使命，粵塾（How to study Cantonese）係一間專門出版廣東話電子書同有聲書嘅公司。我哋嘅目標顧客係嚟自英語系國家、學𡁵廣東話嘅外國人同海外港人。我哋嘅團隊由擁有唔同專長（設計、插畫、配音、動畫、網頁設計、小編、廣東話文法）嘅巴絲（94-97）組成。經過大概10個月嘅努力，我哋開始建立到我哋嘅品牌同產品。<br />\n<br />\n喺大概2個月之前，我哋推出咗第一個系列嘅故事書，《粵譯伊索寓言》。我哋依家想請一個作家幫手寫一個新嘅系列，介紹香港傳奇人物。我哋會負責其他嘢，包括推廣，配音，插畫，排版等等。<br />\n<br />\n我哋想搵嘅人： <br />\n-識寫粵文（重要）<br />\n-寫嘅故事吸引人（重要）<br />\n-有寫兒童故事經驗<br />\n-如果識埋粵拼就perfect<br />\n<br />\n職責：<br />\n- 根據史實好有趣噉用廣東話介紹一個香港傳奇人物嘅事蹟，500-1000字<br />\n- 根據內文整粵拼（唔識我哋會教，放心）<br />\n<br />\n酬勞：<br />\n- 我哋Ebook revenue 嘅 10~15% <br />\n<br />\n如果有興趣，就用telegram或者Facebook聯絡我哋啦。記得畀你之前寫過嘅，好嘅作品我哋睇！<br />\n<br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/fargohighfly\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffargohighfly&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41KDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=e59bac61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/fargohighfly</a> <br />\n<br />\n我哋嘅Facebook page: <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/howtostudycantonese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhowtostudycantonese&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41KDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=7ae23925\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/howtostudycantonese</a><br />\n<br />\n我哋嘅網站: <a href=\"http://www.howtostudycantonese.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.howtostudycantonese.com&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41KDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=5fd3975d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.howtostudycantonese.com</a><br />\n<br />\n我哋之前啲電子書嘅product image:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pVFamLG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpVFamLG.png&h=1ac008e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/znxv6cn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fznxv6cn.png&h=15dd91db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fL1MExn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfL1MExn.png&h=1fd2612a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RwkUOqJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRwkUOqJ.png&h=49dc25d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e48c98790fb68883e0895c44a3c3b46e282d3b70","tid":1492774,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:36:54.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"c58207b73fe1bb495d8d76d44da2f3b75e089196","tid":1492774,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:46:18.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"bf87b1f562070e5524089a56013741f572217240","tid":1492774,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:55:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"300bed7c0b21fb2b84f4b40528ea5ef48c5bbc62","tid":1492774,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:04:01.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"4ae1369906723f21d567cef5327a2cd4371550bf","tid":1492774,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:16:50.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"d71919ba969ba59747fce40fe602f7b519392b9f","tid":1492774,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:40:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"28d7b2c6cd7134fc65bad32dc87ba1e69ba9ef67","tid":1492774,"uid":45280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:51:16.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4faf8fc8d7cab66643577e15be556e4ee1596000","tid":1492774,"uid":223799,"like":0,"di